      <title>IPSOS民意调查显示，支持英国增加国防支出的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/support-for-uk-to-raise-defense-spending-grows-ipsos-poll-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[IPSOS的一项民意调查显示，英国人对英国人的批准增加了国防支出，即使这意味着纳税人的负担更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/support-for-uk-to-raise-defense-spending-grows-ipsos-poll-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 14:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
